## Skills

- **`02-skills/`** — 60+ Claude Desktop skills (hub/spoke). Each has a `SKILL.md` with frontmatter trigger description.
- **`.claude/skills/`** — Claude Code slash commands (`/today`, `/session-end`, `/reconcile`, `/new-project`, `/framework-check`).

Cursor doesn't auto-load skills the way Claude Code does — read any `02-skills/<name>/SKILL.md` directly when a task matches.

## Conventions

- Artifact filenames: `context_descriptor_vN.N_YYYY-MM-DD.ext` — never overwrite, increment version.
- `[[wikilinks]]` for internal connections (Obsidian graph view depends on them).
- YAML frontmatter on metadata-bearing notes. Tags: lowercase + hyphenated.
- Tasks: `- [ ]` open, `- [x]` done.
- Never delete notes — move to `_archive/` subfolders.
- Never commit `04-artifacts/`, `05-version-registers/`, or most of `07-projects/`.

## Surfaces aware of the brain

- **Claude Code** — auto-loads via `.claude/hooks/dispatcher.py` and `CLAUDE.md`
- **Cursor** — this rule (`.cursor/rules/brain.mdc`)
- **Obsidian** — reads the folder as a vault (Templater + Dataview + Git plugins)
- **Claude Desktop** — reads via Desktop Commander MCP

Filesystem is the contract. Whatever any surface writes, all others see on next read.

